        "More and more he is convinced that English is an unfit medium for the truth of South Africa.",
        "Can I guess?' he says. 'Are you trying to remind me of something?' 'Am I trying to remind you of what?' 'Of what women undergo at the hands of men.",
        "A dog will accept the justice of that: a beating for a chewing. But desire is another story. No animal will accept the justice of being punished for following its instincts.",
